706
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:32,270
Jumpa lagi.

707
00:42:39,750 --> 00:42:42,250
Selamat tinggal, saya.

708
00:42:43,330 --> 00:42:44,940
Oh!

709
00:42:58,110 --> 00:43:00,220
Sanada!

710
00:43:08,490 --> 00:43:10,660
Jaga diri.

711
00:43:13,520 --> 00:43:15,010
Ya.

712
00:43:15,010 --> 00:43:17,830
Saya akan balik dengan semangat lusa.

713
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:20,711
"Lusa"?

714
00:43:20,711 --> 00:43:23,350
Ya, saya hanya pergi untuk temu duga kemasukan universiti.

715
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:26,500
Sudo...

716
00:43:27,370 --> 00:43:29,060
Apa?

717
00:43:29,060 --> 00:43:30,690
Tak apa.

718
00:43:30,690 --> 00:43:32,380
Saya dah perasan.

719
00:43:32,380 --> 00:43:33,810
Ya.

