728
00:44:13,750 --> 00:44:15,680
Saya juga.

729
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:20,640
Saya rasa saya akan jatuh cinta pada awak juga.

730
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:24,110
Haraplah.

731
00:44:26,200 --> 00:44:28,150
Apabila awak balik,

732
00:44:28,150 --> 00:44:29,770
